  "texts": [
    "All edges were directed, and some were signed.",
    "Gene-protein and drug-target edges were assumed to be signed and unidirectional.",
    "A positive or negative gene-protein edge indicated that mutations in the gene and resulting protein dysfunction would be positively or negatively associated with AD.",
    "A positive or negative drug-target edge indicated that the drug would activate or inhibit its binding protein.",
    "Protein-protein edges were considered bidirectional by default, except that some were unidirectional according to the PPI data."
